# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資、賭博或做生意嗰陣，當損失達到一定程度時，決定賣出資產或停止操作，以減少進一步嘅損失（量詞：個）
eng:to cut one's losses; to stop trading to limit losses
<eg>
yue:呢隻股票跌咗咁多，我決定止蝕走人。 (nei5 zi1 gu3 dao6 ze2 zo2 do1, ngo5 zeoi6 ding6 zi2 sik1 zau2 jan4.)
eng:I decided to cut my losses and get out of this stock after it dropped so much. [end of text]


